author: Christina Zhao
title: Colorado Health Care Workers Confront Protesters Amid Demonstration Against Stay-at-Home Orders
description: "They were blocking the roads until the police force stepped in," photojournalist Alyson McClaran said.
content:
Health care workers in Denver, Colorado on Sunday confronted demonstrators protesting the stay-at-home orders implemented by state governors to limit the spread of the coronavirus.
